Original Text: 剣術を始めたら剣王になったニャ！
Translated Text: When I started swordsmanship, I became a sword king!

Original Text: 叔母ちゃんはなにをやらせてもうまくできない乱暴者だったけど
Translated Text: Auntie was a violent person who couldn't get anything right.

Original Text: でもひとつだけ例があるニャ！
族長に相応しくなるよう大学に送りこまれたんだろうな．．．
Translated Text: I guess they sent him to college to be worthy of a chief ... .

Original Text: ．．．こいつらは獣神の未裔のクセにアホすぎるから
Translated Text: ... ... These guys are too stupid to be descendants of the beast god.

Original Text: 一般転生公異世界行ったら本気だす
Translated Text: I'll get serious if I go to another world, general reincarnation lord.
